name: Mr. Sridhar Gupta
quote: A project first envisioned by Late Mr. Lakshmiah Shetty and coordinated by Mr. Sridhar Gupta, this structure evolved from a plot to a school and was later transformed into a fully sold-out apartment.

name: Mr. Shankar Lal and Brothers
quote: A family home built for Mr. Shankar Lal and his brothers designed for both unity and privacy. Even after 15 years, they remain happy with the quality and their home.

name: Mrs. Vinutha
quote: It’s been almost 5 years since we moved in and we haven’t faced any issues. No leaks, great ventilation, and the house stays naturally cool. I would confidently recommend building with them.

name: Mrs. Shashikala
quote: The finishing left a strong impression with its quality, craftsmanship and architecture. This 375 sq ft home has stayed well ventilated, and in 13 years it has never felt small. Very nicely built.

name: Mr. Anuj Lunia and Brother
quote: Built in 2006 for Mr. Anuj Lunia and his brother, this project features two duplex homes on a single plot. Nearly 20 years later, the structure still stands strong without a repaint, reflecting the durability, quality and minimal maintenance that define our work.

name: Mr. Srinath
quote: I met Sridhar Naidu 15 years ago and immediately knew he would build my home. Four years ago he did and I’m very happy with the quality.

name: Mr. Vinay & Narayana
quote: We wanted a bright, spacious and clutter free home with strong rental yield, and they made it happen. We are very happy!
